FBIS4-251 "drafr066_e_94002" FBIS-AFR-94-066 Daily Report 6 Apr 1994 WEST AFRICA Niger Parliamentary Sessions Resume; Opposition Stays Away Parliamentary Sessions Resume; Opposition Stays Away AB0604144594 Niamey Voix du Sahel Network in French 0545 GMT 6 Apr 94 AB0604144594 Niamey Voix du Sahel Network French BFN [Text] The National Assembly has resumed sittings without the parliamentary opposition which is boycotting the sittings. The speaker yesterday appealed to members of the opposition parliamentary group to return to their seats.
